OL,5, Lionel Messi's Hong Kong fans who      
OL,6, bought tickets to a friendly that he   
OL,7, skipped at the last minute will get a  
OL,8, 50% refund, the match organiser said.  
OL,10,FMessi's absence from the game in       
OL,11,FFebruary, which he blamed on an injury,
OL,12,Fsent Chinse fans seething for weeks.   
OL,14,FTicketholders applying for refunds must
OL,15,Fagree not to pursue legal action,      
OL,16,FTatler Asia said.                      
OL,18,FThe refunds could cost up to HK$56m    
OL,19,F(#5.6m; $7.1m), the publication said.  
